    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are calling Activity.this from an inner class, you have to put <strong>inner</strong> before the class</p>\n\n<pre><code>class MyActivity : MainActivity() {\n    // Call from class itself\n    val builder = MaterialDialog.Builder(this@MyActivity) \n\n    inner class Inner {\n        this@MyActivity // Call from the inner class \n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
