    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><code>getActivity()</code> equivalent is <code>this@activity_name</code> \nin case of builder for materialDialog</p>\n\n<pre><code>materialDialog = MaterialDialog.Builder(this)\n</code></pre>\n"
