    "question_id" : 41617042,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can get the object of activity like this.</p>\n<pre><code>class DemoActivity : BaseActivity() {\n    val builder = MaterialDialog.Builder(this@DemoActivity)\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 11562480,
      "reputation" : 7868,
      "user_id" : 8471798,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/IcOEkVWk.png?s=256",
